title: UNIMPLEMENTED: DNN library is not found.
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

This morning i started getting an issue with my Colab notebook, after having it working for days.

I have the following dependencies installed:

!pip install deeplabcut
!pip install opencv-python-headless==4.4.0.46

Everything works up until training the dataset. Then i receive a DNN library not found error.

Starting training....
